snippet.title: College Football USA 96
snippet.description: The first game with all the Division 1-A teams (at the time), fun game, I think this is also the first game to use the real bowl names... this is the Sega Genesis version... probably my 2nd favorite college football game behind NCAA 06... which will probably always be my favorite.
